<title>yạ rb ạ̉nt wḥdk</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- (yạ rb ạ̉nt wḥdk .. fyk ʿzạʾ qlby
 mạ mn mrẗ ṭlbtk .. ạ̹lạ wtnjyny)2
 ạlqrạr- (qlbk klh ḥnạn .. yạ rb yạ ḥnạn)2
 (ạ̹n nsyt ạlạ̉m rḍyʿhạ .. ạ̉nt lạ tnsy̱)2
 2- (ạ̹n wqʿt fy ḍyqẗ .. wạlạ̉ʿdạʾ ḥwạlyã
 ạ̉lạqyk rby ḥbyby .. mạsk bydyã)2
 3- (wạ̹n ạ̹blys ạ̉tạny .. wqʿny fy ạlkẖṭyẗ
 tyjy ạ̹nt yạ rby .. wtmnḥny ạlḥryẗ)2
 4- (wạ̹n ṭlbt ṭlbẗ .. tstjyb lyã
 btfrḥny dwmaⁿạ .. wtmsḥ ly ʿynyã)2
 5- (wʿdt wqlt yạ rby .. dạymaⁿạ ạ̉nạ mʿkm
 wạ̹n knt ạ̉nạ mʿạkm .. sẖwfwạ myn ʿlykm)2</lyrics>
